name: Wrapped Axelar
description: Axelar powers the interchain future. Axelar is a programmable blockchain interoperability layer that spans all of Web3. That means application users can interact with any asset, any application, on any chain, with one click. You can think of it as Stripe for Web3. Developers interact with a simple API atop a permissionless network that routes messages and ensures network security via proof-of-stake consensus.
